astal is my beat, and I bring the best of both to everyone I work with.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"phil-image\"][vc_single_image image=\"112\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"500x500\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Philosophy + Approach','','publish','open','open','','philosophy-approach','','','2015-03-19 19:24:47','2015-03-19 19:24:47','',0,'http://abbot-water.dev/?page_id=10',5,'page','',0),
