e branding, content and media strategies that complement DR activities, to build targeted awareness and drive revenue.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][themestudio_title title=\"Publishers / Ad Tech\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Brand-side marketing insight can help you differentiate yourself when fighting for ad dollars. Together we’ll focus on business development efforts to enrich your brand and agency relationships, develop new ad offerings and unlock video, content and native, all with monetization in mind.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_text_separator title=\"SERVICES\" title_align=\"separator_align_center\" align=\"align_center\" color=\"grey\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_service_shortcode posts_per_page=\"8\" has_boder=\"yes\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Services','','publish','closed','closed','','services','','','2015-03-19 18:48:36','2015-03-19 18:48:36','',0,'http://abbot-water.dev/?page_id=12',4,'page','',0),
