	(32,1,'2015-03-05 21:50:56','2015-03-05 21:50:56','Abbot + Water sits at the intersection of tech, strategy, media and marketing, from NYC to LA and everywhere in between. We work with a broad clientele of brands, publishers, ad tech companies and start-ups as digital marketing experts with a focus on content, video and media.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBrands\r\n\r\nConsider us your Digital SWAT team. We’ll marry your marketing and digital plans with informed, innovative and results-driven digital strategies, proven to be effective across the paid, owned and earned landscape.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nPublishers / Ad Tech\r\n\r\nBrand-side marketing insight can help you differentiate yourself when fighting for ad dollars. Together we’ll enrich your brand and agency relationships, develop new ad offerings and unlock video, content and native, with monetization in mind.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nStart-ups / Emerging Brands\r\n\r\nCreative and scrappy – our specialty when working with start-ups. If you have a product, and funding, it’s time to build your brand. We’ll create content and media strategies that complement DR activities, to build targeted awareness and drive revenue.\r\n\r\nServices:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Content Marketing &amp; Distribution</span>:  The lines between brands and publishers have never been blurrier, but the issues are clear – you need eyeballs on the editorial content you are creating. Simply put – I help clients craft strategic marketing and distribution strategies that drive engagement with the content you spend time and money creating, then measure the impact of those efforts to the business with solid KPIs.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Video Strategy</span>: How do you navigate a fragmented, cluttered  and messy landscape? With expertise and education. We’ll start with an overview of the video landscape, then move on to tailored navigation of and strategy for video your content and advertising, across devices, platforms and publishers.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Brand Building</span>: You’ve got a product, you’ve got funding. Now you need to build a brand, build awareness, and generate revenue. I’ll leverage my billion-dollar-brand marketing experience to develop innovative strategies, materials and content, targeted to your audience, in an efficient and scrappy way, to complement DR marketing and other lower-funnel activities.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Media Strategy</span>:  Banners, search, social, video, high-impact, programmatic, mobile – there are many cookie-cutter media plans out there by accident and by design. With a depth of knowledge across online and offline media, I build strategies for effective investment that support, and impact, brand goals.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Ad Product Development &amp; Monetization</span>: As a Publisher or Ad Tech Vendor, Brand Marketer attention, and advertising dollars, can be hard to get! I\'ll leverage my +12-year brand-side career to create marketable and differentiated ad products for you, while unlocking new revenue streams around content, video and native. As the recipient of countless pitches, I’ve seen the good, the bad and the ugly. I can help you avoid those last two categories while enriching your selling efforts, creating ROI for brand and agency clients, with monetization in mind.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Communications Planning and Social Marketing:</span> At the intersection of PR, Marketing and Influencers, you need synthesized communications and social marketing planning. I’ll help you coordinate across teams, departments and agencies to determine how and where to communicate, with tailored content and a solid amplification plan, both must-haves in the PR and social stratosphere.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Innovation and Emerging Tech</span>:  Does your team have a Digital Inspiration Pipeline? How do you operationalize innovation? I curate the emerging tech landscape, providing strategic counsel on relevant trends, while crafting tailored test-and-learn opportunities for brands big and small.</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Resource Management:</span> How can you get the most out of your resource and agency partners? As a cross-functional leader, I’ve managed teams across agencies, brands and publishers to accomplish projects that can span weeks, months or years. With honed communication skills and detail-focused project management, no team is too big (or too small) to be productive.</li>\r\n</ul>','Services','','inherit','open','open','','12-revision-v1','','','2015-03-05 21:50:56','2015-03-05 21:50:56','',12,'http://abbot-water.dev/2015/03/05/12-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
