	(39,1,'2015-03-05 22:13:55','2015-03-05 22:13:55','<h3>Philosophy</h3>\r\n<p>I’m not a digital marketer; I’m a marketer with digital expertise. I founded my consultancy because I am fiercely passionate about what I do, and I believe there is tremendous opportunity to succeed across the paid, owned and earned landscape. By marrying the best of emerging tech, strategy, media and marketing, I help organizations develop holistic and integrated strategies, built to evolve as the landscape shifts, to drive current and future goals. The results: laser-focused efforts that drive engagement and ROI.</p>\r\n<h3>Approach</h3>\r\n<p>Why Abbot + Water? The name represents my approach – a little bit NYC, a little bit LA – and it sounds cool. But most importantly, it represents the digital world we’re doing business in. Digital isn’t a NYC thing – it’s an everywhere thing. Digital is my expertise, bicoastal is my beat, and I bring the best of both to everyone I work with.</p>','Philosophy + Approach','','inherit','open','open','','10-revision-v1','','','2015-03-05 22:13:55','2015-03-05 22:13:55','',10,'http://abbot-water.dev/2015/03/05/10-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
