	(69,1,'2015-03-09 20:16:08','2015-03-09 20:16:08','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_title title=\"Philosophy\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"]asdasdasdasd[/themestudio_title][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Philosophy</h3>\r\nI’m not a digital marketer; I’m a marketer with digital expertise. I founded my consultancy because I am fiercely passionate about what I do, and I believe there is tremendous opportunity to succeed across the paid, owned and earned landscape. By marrying the best of emerging tech, strategy, media and marketing, I help organizations develop holistic and integrated strategies, built to evolve as the landscape shifts, to drive current and future goals. The results: laser-focused efforts that drive engagement and ROI.\r\n<h3>Approach</h3>\r\nWhy Abbot + Water? The name represents my approach – a little bit NYC, a little bit LA – and it sounds cool. But most importantly, it represents the digital world we’re doing business in. Digital isn’t a NYC thing – it’s an everywhere thing. Digital is my expertise, bicoastal is my beat, and I bring the best of both to everyone I work with.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Philosophy + Approach','','inherit','open','open','','10-revision-v1','','','2015-03-09 20:16:08','2015-03-09 20:16:08','',10,'http://abbot-water.dev/?p=69',0,'revision','',0),
