	(76,1,'2015-03-09 21:19:04','2015-03-09 21:19:04','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Abbot + Water sits at the intersection of tech, strategy, media and marketing, from NYC to LA and everywhere in between. We work with a broad clientele of brands, publishers, ad tech companies and start-ups as digital marketing experts with a focus on content, video and media.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_title title=\"Brands\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Consider us your Digital SWAT team. We’ll marry your marketing and digital plans with informed, innovative and results-driven digital strategies, proven to be effective across the paid, owned and earned landscape.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_title title=\"Publishers / Ad Tech\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Brand-side marketing insight can help you differentiate yourself when fighting for ad dollars. Together we’ll enrich your brand and agency relationships, develop new ad offerings and unlock video, content and native, with monetization in mind.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_title title=\"Start-Ups / Emerging Brands\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Creative and scrappy – our specialty when working with start-ups. If you have a product, and funding, it’s time to build your brand. We’ll create content and media strategies that complement DR activities, to build targeted awareness and drive revenue.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Services','','inherit','open','open','','12-revision-v1','','','2015-03-09 21:19:04','2015-03-09 21:19:04','',12,'http://abbot-water.dev/2015/03/09/12-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
