	(87,1,'2015-03-10 15:31:10','2015-03-10 15:31:10','<em>How can you get the most out of your resource and agency partners?</em> What’s the best way to craft and evaluate an RFP? Depending on your needs, I’ll help you source and evaluate resources to create an effective cross-agency or cross-organization team. As a marketing leader, I’ve managed teams across agencies, brands and publishers to accomplish projects that can span weeks, months or years. With honed communication skills and detail-focused project management, no team is too big <em>(or too small)</em> to be productive.','Resource Management','','publish','closed','closed','','resource-management','','','2015-03-12 13:39:34','2015-03-12 13:39:34','',0,'http://abbot-water.dev/?post_type=service&#038;p=87',0,'service','',0),
	(88,1,'2015-03-10 15:31:59','2015-03-10 15:31:59','In an Apple Watch, OTT, IOT What’s App world, staying current is not optional, it’s a necessity. Crafting relevant test-and-learns is just as important when budgets are tight and expectations are high. Every quarter, I’ll synthesize and report on the emerging tech landscape to provide your team with a short list of companies to watch, relevant to your business goals. Then, we’ll create tailored pilot projects, with clear objectives and measurement, to move your organization forward.','Innovation Trend Reporting + Pilots','','publish','closed','closed','','innovation-trend-reporting-pilots','','','2015-03-12 13:38:13','2015-03-12 13:38:13','',0,'http://abbot-water.dev/?post_type=service&#038;p=88',0,'service','',0),
	(89,1,'2015-03-10 15:32:38','2015-03-10 15:32:38','At the intersection of PR, Marketing and Influencers, you need synthesized communications and social marketing planning. I’ll help you coordinate across teams, departments and agencies to determine how and where to communicate, with tailored content and a solid amplification plan, both must-haves in the PR and social stratosphere. ','Communications Planning + Social Marketing','','publish','closed','closed','','communications-planning-social-marketing','','','2015-03-10 15:32:38','2015-03-10 15:32:38','',0,'http://abbot-water.dev/?post_type=service&#038;p=89',0,'service','',0),
	(90,1,'2015-03-10 15:34:15','2015-03-10 15:34:15','As a Publisher or Ad Tech Vendor, Brand Marketer attention, and advertising dollars, can be hard to get. I\'ll leverage my +12-year brand-side career to co-create marketable and differentiated ad products with you, while unlocking new revenue streams around content, video and native. As the recipient of countless pitches, I’ve seen the good, the bad and the ugly. Let\'s avoid those last two categories while enriching your selling efforts, creating ROI for brand and agency clients.','Business Development + Monetization','','publish','closed','closed','','business-development-monetization','','','2015-03-12 13:36:28','2015-03-12 13:36:28','',0,'http://abbot-water.dev/?post_type=service&#038;p=90',0,'service','',0),
	(91,1,'2015-03-10 15:35:25','2015-03-10 15:35:25','Banners, search, social, video, high-impact, programmatic, mobile – there are many cookie-cutter media plans out there by accident and by design. With a depth of knowledge across online and offline media, I’ll build bespoke strategies for effective investment, then evaluate publisher proposals and agency plans to ensure they that support, and impact, brand goals.','Media + Channel Strategy','','publish','closed','closed','','media-channel-strategy','','','2015-03-12 13:34:13','2015-03-12 13:34:13','',0,'http://abbot-water.dev/?post_type=service&#038;p=91',0,'service','',0),
	(92,1,'2015-03-10 15:35:52','2015-03-10 15:35:52','You’ve got a product, you’ve got funding. Now you need to build a brand, build awareness, and generate revenue. I’ll leverage my billion-dollar-brand marketing experience to develop innovative strategies, materials and content, targeted to your audience, in an efficient and scrappy way, to complement DR marketing and other lower-funnel activities. ','Brand Strategy','','publish','closed','closed','','brand-strategy','','','2015-03-12 13:33:08','2015-03-12 13:33:08','',0,'http://abbot-water.dev/?post_type=service&#038;p=92',0,'service','',0),
	(93,1,'2015-03-10 15:36:27','2015-03-10 15:36:27','<em>How do you navigate a fragmented, cluttered  and messy landscape?</em> With expertise and education. We’ll start with an overview of the video landscape, then move on to tailored navigation of and strategy for video your content and advertising, across devices, platforms and publishers.','Video Strategy','','publish','closed','closed','','video-strategy','','','2015-03-10 15:37:30','2015-03-10 15:37:30','',0,'http://abbot-water.dev/?post_type=service&#038;p=93',0,'service','',0),
	(94,1,'2015-03-10 15:36:54','2015-03-10 15:36:54','The lines between brands and publishers have never been blurrier, but the issues are clear – you need eyeballs on the editorial content you are creating. Simply put – I help clients craft strategic marketing and distribution strategies that drive engagement with the content you spend time and money creating, then measure the impact of those efforts to the business with solid KPIs.  ','Content Marketing + Distribution','','publish','closed','closed','','content-marketing-distribution','','','2015-03-10 15:36:54','2015-03-10 15:36:54','',0,'http://abbot-water.dev/?post_type=service&#038;p=94',0,'service','',0),
	(95,1,'2015-03-10 15:46:41','2015-03-10 15:46:41','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Abbot + Water sits at the intersection of tech, strategy, media and marketing, from NYC to LA and everywhere in between. We work with a broad clientele of brands, publishers, ad tech companies and start-ups as digital marketing experts with a focus on content, video and media.</h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"15px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][themestudio_title title=\"Brands\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Consider us your Digital SWAT team. We’ll marry your marketing and digital plans with informed, innovative and results-driven digital strategies, proven to be effective across the paid, owned and earned landscape.</p>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][themestudio_title title=\"Publishers / Ad Tech\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Brand-side marketing insight can help you differentiate yourself when fighting for ad dollars. Together we’ll enrich your brand and agency relationships, develop new ad offerings and unlock video, content and native, with monetization in mind.</p>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][themestudio_title title=\"Start-Ups / Emerging Brands\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Creative and scrappy – our specialty when working with start-ups. If you have a product, and funding, it’s time to build your brand. We’ll create content and media strategies that complement DR activities, to build targeted awareness and drive revenue.</p>\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"32px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_text_separator title=\"SERVICES\" title_align=\"separator_align_center\" align=\"align_center\" color=\"grey\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row gmbt_prlx_bg_type=\"parallax\" gmbt_prlx_break_parents=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_smooth_scrolling=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_mute=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_loop_trigger=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_video_aspect_ratio=\"16:9\" gmbt_prlx_parallax=\"none\" gmbt_prlx_speed=\"0.3\" gmbt_prlx_enable_mobile=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_service_shortcode posts_per_page=\"8\" has_boder=\"yes\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Services','','inherit','open','open','','12-revision-v1','','','2015-03-10 15:46:41','2015-03-10 15:46:41','',12,'http://abbot-water.dev/?p=95',0,'revision','',0),
	(96,1,'2015-03-10 15:55:07','2015-03-10 15:55:07','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row gmbt_prlx_bg_type=\"parallax\" gmbt_prlx_break_parents=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_smooth_scrolling=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_mute=\"\" gmbt_prlx_video_youtube_loop_trigger=\"0\" gmbt_prlx_video_aspect_ratio=\"16:9\" gmbt_prlx_parallax=\"none\" gmbt_prlx_speed=\"0.3\" gmbt_prlx_enable_mobile=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"34\" alignment=\"center\" border_color=\"black\" img_link_large=\"\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"500x667\" style=\"vc_box_border\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][themestudio_title title=\"Heather Bergstein\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"]President + Chief Strategist[/themestudio_title][vc_column_text]A results-driven digital brand marketing and media expert, Heather Bergstein has spent over a decade working with global Beauty and Fashion companies including L’Oreal, Ralph Lauren and Estee Lauder. Heather’s career began in traditional marketing, and that remains to be the foundation of her approach; she’s not a digital marketer, but a marketer with digital expertise.\r\n\r\nAs President and Chief Strategist of <strong>Abbot + Water</strong>, Heather works with brands, start-ups and publishers as a dot connector, cross-functional leader, and digital swat team of one, creating tailored and informed strategies that drive engagement and ROI, built to evolve in an ever-changing marketing landscape.\r\n\r\nA passionate digital leader, Heather is a frequent panelist and industry participant with a focus on digital content, video and media strategy; her activities, honors awards speak to her dedication. She is based in NYC, where she lives with her son, and bounces between NYC and Santa Monica (aka Silicon Beach), to stay on the pulse of media, tech and everything in between, coast to coast.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][themestudio_title title=\"Activities, Honors + Awards\" align=\"align-center\" text_align=\"center\" title_color=\"#252525\" underline_color=\"#252525\"][/themestudio_title][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">• Brand Innovators 40 Under 40, Class of 2013\r\n• Editorial Board Member, Journal of Business to Consumer Marketing\r\n• Internet Week 2014 Panelist, OMMA Social\r\n• Member, IAB MIXX Screening Committee, 2013 and 2014\r\n• Co-Founder, The Cabernet Group\r\n• Volunteer Content Contributor, Taste of Tribeca\r\n• Upcoming Panelist: Click Z Live NYC 2015\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Bio + Credentials','','inherit','open','open','','8-revision-v1','','','2015-03-10 15:55:07','2015-03-10 15:55:07','',8,'http://abbot-water.dev/?p=96',0,'revision','',0),
